{"tid":2026017,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港女子28年前買入深圳單位一直丟空,近日發現竟有人居住","createTime":"2020-05-20T15:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T16:10:36.000Z","uid":65710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3457bc306ba8046456eac54c228168b8c56b1914","tid":2026017,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sfADcpfB6hk&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsfADcpfB6hk%26t%3D3s&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=676ab84c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sfADcpfB6hk&amp;t=3s</a><br />\n<br />\n28年前香港的張女士以33萬買入深圳華天花園一個約1500呎的單位，但多年來丟空，近年這單位已升值到600萬元。張女士早前托親戚幫她看看單位情況，怎知發現單位不單裝修了，還在2001年起被別人住了。<br />\n<br />\n為何不可以直接趕他們走呢？原來張女士當年買樓的時候，只有一張買賣合同和手寫的收據，之後一直無去補辦房產證，無辦法證明自己是業主。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要補辦房產證都有難度，因為屋苑原本的發展商已被收購，無辦法幫他們辦理。<br />\n<br />\n至於目前的住戶又怎得到房屋呢?居民傳他們是撬門入去，但住戶否認，話他們一家也是從別人手中購得單位的。社區綜治辦指住戶曾出示過轉讓合同。<br />\n<br />\n張女士的親戚目前正和原發展商和收購商，協商補辦相關證明和房產證，他指只要住戶肯搬，就既往不咎。現住戶就指，只要張女士證明到房屋是她的，願意跟對方談處理方法。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 有線新聞組"},{"pid":"119530c5e002b5aa45413ee0dd6b6954d0a89dfc","tid":2026017,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"張女士想搏懵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75d9bbc88e0bc5312e7361470054d7f41cb71dd","tid":2026017,"uid":135408,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"同支那人講合約？收皮啦"},{"pid":"1617ff58b7eb3a26a782eeebd96fe6823f739199","tid":2026017,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"抵啦 返大陸住啦張小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d9116170670bb8333f46ef09100287dc57a5a1","tid":2026017,"uid":36702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"有咩問題   <br />\n<br />\n大家血濃於水   借間屋住下有咩問題先<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔得   即係唔認自己係中國人  想搞港獨啦"},{"pid":"1243af8765e9a0777a57d0ee7b792e0a7b990c65","tid":2026017,"uid":21895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"一屋兩制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec2c3e7919715018a49df68a688dd897ed9cf10","tid":2026017,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">現住戶就指，只要張女士證明到房屋是她的，願意跟對方談處理方法。</span><br />\n<br />\n以支那人的態度， 住客肯定係撬門入去白住"},{"pid":"86d244155750829929a17625babbaed5bfcbcebe","tid":2026017,"uid":112241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"幫佢住返的人氣wo,起麻俾返人一千幾百萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ca4b7f282febbebf32b7179ffff0336a08e291","tid":2026017,"uid":18177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"28年都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話大陸啦，香港都有逆權侵佔"}]}